Run the following command in {{project_name_short}} Template.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo systemctl restart qubes-whonix-torified-updates-proxy-check
}}

{{IconSet|h1|4}} Then try to update or use <code>apt</code> again.

{{CodeSelect|code=
